CatDescriptText: Mrs. Constance Smith's sons are Dalton and Ernie Smith, and daughters Mary Smith and Edythe Smith Perkins.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four men and six women, including Dalton Smith on left, unknown, Mary Smith, Constance Smith, Ernie Smith, unknown, and Edythe Smith Perkins, standing behind table with flowers, candles, and wrapped gifts, for honorary celebration of Constance Smith by Ebenezer Baptist Church Missionary Group, in interior of Ebenezer Baptist Church
